TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Generalization of the Open Expanding Economy Model
AU  - Moeschlin, Otto
AB  - [The existence of an equilibrium solution for the open expanding economy model of Morgenstern-Thompson is proven under weaker assumptions than originally used.The proof is based on a theorem of the Farkas type formulated for finite dimensional linear spaces ordered by means of cones.]
